@lianna, but not: Those instances are usually small to medium and you can post about whatever, not just anime and cute. They are nice because they usually have a friendly culture. It's easy to find accepting people to talk about whatever.
niu.moe is probably the most famous of those but it's going to close in March. I don't think there are a lot of people left there.

I prefer not to say who I thought you were because it would make it much easier to associate this persona with the one I use there. But it was someone nice, don't worry. :3
